== Mikawa Seven Lucky Gods == '''Mikawa Seven Lucky Gods''' (三河七福神, Mikawa Shichifukujin) is a pilgrimage route consisting of seven [[:en:Buddhist temple|temples]] in the [[:en:Mikawa Province|Mikawa Province]] region of [[:en:Aichi Prefecture|Aichi Prefecture]], dedicated to the [[:en:Seven Lucky Gods|Seven Lucky Gods]].
